score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eckermann\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Peter_Eckermann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Peter_Eckermann\"}, {\"begin\": 736, \"end\": 740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King\", \"score\": 0.6120307087465529, \"rank\": 0.5656843840181455, \"text\": \"King\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'He's changed his mind, he went to go forward,' BBC commentator Andy Austin said as the run began to go wrong.\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 1005, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.8815004965262575, \"rank\": 0.13436703040982073, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 959, \"end\": 970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Austin_(sport_shooter)\", \"score\": 0.9999749248008114, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andy Austin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Austin_(sport_shooter)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Austin_(sport_shooter)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'This is unbelievably strange and bad riding from Henrik von Eckermann.\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1056, \"end\": 1076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_von_Eckermann\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Henrik von Eckermann\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_von_Eckermann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_von_Eckermann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'What is he doing?!\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1098, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's fallen off.\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never seen anything like this in my life.\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1164, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the world No.1, he completely messed up his ride.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just wanted to show this video of Henrik von Eckermann, the world no.1.\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1295, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1258, \"end\": 1278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_von_Eckermann\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Henrik von Eckermann\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_von_Eckermann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_von_Eckermann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not into horse riding so I have no clue what happened here if anyone can tell me.#Olympics2024Paris#Olympics#Equestrianpic.twitter.com/OomqSBMLbW  'What is going on?\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1461, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He changed his mind and it completely unsettled and spooked King Edward.\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1522, \"end\": 1526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King\", \"score\": 0.6120307087465529, \"rank\": 0.5656843840181455, \"text\": \"King\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was out of control when he jumped the number eight.\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have never seen drama like it.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Extraordinary.\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Henrik thankfully looks okay, so does the horse.\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'He makes a terrible mistake, rides quite crazily out of control to the fence and then falls off because his horse spooks.\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1812, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'You could not make it up.\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you wanted to tune in for some drama, you are certainly getting it.\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1911, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was quite unbelievable.'\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Von Eckermann looked shocked and a little dazed following the fall but he and King Edward were thankfully unharmed and left the arena together.\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 2086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1947, \"end\": 1956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Peter_Eckermann\", \"score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eckermann\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Peter_Eckermann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Peter_Eckermann\"}, {\"begin\": 2021, \"end\": 2025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King\", \"score\": 0.6120307087465529, \"rank\": 0.5656843840181455, \"text\": \"King\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just before Von Eckermann took to the course he was described as the 'most bankable rider' in the showjumping final.\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2204, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2104, \"end\": 2113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Peter_Eckermann\", \"score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eckermann\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Peter_Eckermann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Peter_Eckermann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'One thing is for sure, this guy is not going to be fazed, even at this stage of the competition,' another commentator said before the dramatic fall.\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2355, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'He's not going to be fazed.\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2385, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's got nerves of steel and a horse with talent, over to you, Henrik von Eckermann.\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2470, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We said we wasn't going to do big build-ups but we just had to with this pair.'\", \"from\": 2472, \"to\": 2552, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 is Von Eckermann's third Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2554, \"end\": 2564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999911324, \"rank\": 8.949190233240112e-12, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2572, \"end\": 2581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Peter_Eckermann\", \"score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eckermann\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Peter_Eckermann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Peter_Eckermann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At Tokyo the two-time world champion won gold in the team event and finished fourth in the individual competition.\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2608, \"end\": 2613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.99998920001883, \"rank\": 1.0332808798906521e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2769, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympic pole vaulter off